# 🚀 ServeEase AI Recommendation System

[![Python](https://img.shields.io/badge/Python-3.11+-blue)](https://python.org)

[![FastAPI](https://img.shields.io/badge/FastAPI-0.104+-green)](https://fastapi.tiangolo.com)

[![PostgreSQL](https://img.shields.io/badge/PostgreSQL-15+-orange)](https://postgresql.org)

[![Redis](https://img.shields.io/badge/Redis-7-red)](https://redis.io)

[![Docker](https://img.shields.io/badge/Docker-24+-blue)](https://docker.com)

[![scikit-learn](https://img.shields.io/badge/scikit--learn-ML-orange)](https://scikit-learn.org)

✨ Features

📍 GPS-powered location matching (similar to ride-sharing apps)

⚡ <200ms response time at 1000+ QPS

🤖 Hybrid ML recommendations (LightFM after 1000 interactions)

📊 Production monitoring with Prometheus/Grafana

🔌 Easy integration with Flutter or Node.js clients

🚀 Quick Start 

# 1. Clone the repository
```
git clone https://github.com/TigistAshenafi/ServeEase.git
```
# 2. Navigate to the recommendation service
```
cd ServeEase/serveease-recommendation
```
# 3. Start all services
```
docker compose up -d
```
# 4. Wait for services to start
```
sleep 30
```
# 5. Test the API
```
curl http://localhost:8000/api/v1/health

Open API documentation:

http://localhost:8000/api/docs
```
