🔗 Integration Example
```
Flutter Client Example
final response = await http.get(
  Uri.parse('http://your-server:8000/api/v1/recommendations')
      .replace(queryParameters: {
        'lat': '40.7128',
        'lng': '-74.0060',
        'radius': '10'
      }),
);
```

📊 API Endpoints

| Endpoint               | Description                   |
| ---------------------- | ----------------------------- |
| `GET /health`          | System health status          |
| `GET /recommendations` | Get provider recommendations  |
| `GET /providers/{id}`  | Provider details              |
| `GET /metrics`         | Prometheus monitoring metrics |

🏗️ System Architecture
```
Flutter App
     │
     ▼
Python FastAPI Service (Port 8000)
     │
     ├── PostgreSQL + PostGIS
     │
     └── Redis Cache
```
